  "title": "English Teacher",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Our Education Centre seeks a dedicated part-time English teacher to deliver engaging lessons to primary school students twice weekly, each session lasting 2 hours. The centre has 20 years of industry experience and provides training to support your success.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Deliver structured and engaging English lessons to primary school students twice a week, each lasting 2 hours, to enhance their language skills</li><li>Apply teaching techniques that foster student participation and comprehension in a classroom setting</li><li>Collaborate with the Education Centre team to align lesson content with curriculum standards and student needs</li><li>Participate in training sessions provided by the centre to continuously improve teaching effectiveness and student outcomes</li></ul>",
